      "cookedHtml": "<p>We have a new KITCHEN SINK app to show how to use our SDK, different app features, and learn tricky concepts like pagination.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://auth.monday.com/oauth2/authorize?client_id=b1332d51359f7c186787f045f2cf6cb6&amp;response_type=install\">Install the app here.</a></p>\n<p></p><div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/3X/d/0/d0bcbe5efc19ec65203ba609a5a1a4a3528fef2d.jpeg\" title=\"kitchen-sink-app-preview-image\"><img src=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/optimized/3X/d/0/d0bcbe5efc19ec65203ba609a5a1a4a3528fef2d_2_690x393.jpeg\" alt=\"kitchen-sink-app-preview-image\" width=\"690\" height=\"393\" /><div class=\"meta\"><span class=\"filename\">kitchen-sink-app-preview-image</span><span class=\"informations\">1920×1095 115 KB</span></div></a></div><p></p>\n<hr />\n<h3><a name=\"p-204093-it-contains-17-code-samples-each-showing-a-different-part-of-our-sdk-and-api-1\" class=\"anchor\" href=\"#p-204093-it-contains-17-code-samples-each-showing-a-different-part-of-our-sdk-and-api-1\"></a>It contains 17 code samples, each showing a different part of our SDK and API:</h3>\n<p><img src=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/3X/0/f/0f449c2f331369ead556e3a11751433ac08f21a0.gif\" alt=\"kitchen sink examples\" width=\"690\" height=\"380\" class=\"animated\" /></p>\n<hr />\n<h3><a name=\"p-204093-it-bundles-10-different-app-features-including-ai-assistant-board-item-menus-2\" class=\"anchor\" href=\"#p-204093-it-bundles-10-different-app-features-including-ai-assistant-board-item-menus-2\"></a>It bundles 10 different app features, including AI assistant &amp; board item menus:</h3>\n<p></p><div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/3X/b/b/bb3889f0c321a3962c57c20c85d474c909a8708d.jpeg\" title=\"image\"><img src=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/optimized/3X/b/b/bb3889f0c321a3962c57c20c85d474c909a8708d_2_345x198.jpeg\" alt=\"image\" width=\"345\" height=\"198\" /><div class=\"meta\"><span class=\"filename\">image</span><span class=\"informations\">1210×696 59.8 KB</span></div></a></div><p></p>\n<hr />\n<h3><a name=\"p-204093-you-can-copy-the-sample-code-without-touching-github-3\" class=\"anchor\" href=\"#p-204093-you-can-copy-the-sample-code-without-touching-github-3\"></a>You can copy the sample code without touching Github:</h3>\n<p></p><div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/3X/d/9/d9b9fe19778885fec49fbde35cdefd34fa037b9f.png\" title=\"image\"><img src=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/optimized/3X/d/9/d9b9fe19778885fec49fbde35cdefd34fa037b9f_2_690x355.png\" alt=\"image\" width=\"690\" height=\"355\" /><div class=\"meta\"><span class=\"filename\">image</span><span class=\"informations\">2278×1174 352 KB</span></div></a></div><p></p>\n<hr />\n<h1><a name=\"p-204093-how-to-install-and-use-4\" class=\"anchor\" href=\"#p-204093-how-to-install-and-use-4\"></a>How to install and use</h1>\n<p><a href=\"https://auth.monday.com/oauth2/authorize?client_id=b1332d51359f7c186787f045f2cf6cb6&amp;response_type=install\">You can use this link to install the app.</a></p>\n<p>Once installed, you can add one of the app features to your board, or use the “Sample boards” template to get going. <a href=\"https://github.com/yuhgto/monday-kitchen-sink/blob/main/README.md\">Use this document for detailed instructions on how to get started.</a></p>\n<p>If you want to inspect the sample code or run it locally - <a href=\"https://github.com/yuhgto/monday-kitchen-sink\">Check out the app on Github</a></p>\n<p>Happy building!</p>"
